==============================
 Vagrant: simple test harness
==============================

Use ``make`` and ``git diff`` for a simple test harness for Vagrant-based environment.

Prerequisites
-------------

Dependencies
~~~~~~~~~~~~

- make
- git


Running
-------

Command
~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: shell

    $ make test


Credit
------

This is based on https://chrismorgan.info/blog/make-and-git-diff-test-harness blog post.
